## Session keys (critical)

| Key | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `warehouse_id` | Selected store; set at login or default `exotic_address.is_default=1` |
| `pos_customer_id` | Checkout customer (`vp_customers.id`) |
| `x_api_euid`, `x_api_jwt`, `x_api_browsehistory`, `x_api_etd`, `x_api_etd_pincode` | Exotic retail API session (updated by `RetailApiClient`) |
| `pos_exotic_cart_coupon_details` / `discount_coupon` | Coupon string for cart GET query + header |
| `pos_exotic_cart_custom_reduce` | Custom/cash discount sent to `/cart/addcustomdiscount` |
| `pos_last_checkout_receipt` | Last receipt row for confirmation page |
| `pos_order_create_api_debug` | Last order/create request/response for debug UI |

On `index()` load, legacy cart discount session keys are cleared so each register session starts clean.

