## Checkout flow (`checkout-create`)

See **`pos-order-payment-invoice.mdc`** for full order creation, payment splits, COD, receipt numbering, vp_orders import, and invoice (proforma/final) logic.

Summary:

```
Payment modal submit → checkout-create → order/create (Exotic) → pos_payments rows
  → finalizePosReceiptInvoice (import + auto invoice) → checkout-receipt
```

