## Post-checkout

See **`pos-order-payment-invoice.mdc`** §2–3 for payments and invoice details.

| Step | Action | Result |
|------|--------|--------|
| Receipt page | `checkout-receipt` | `order_confirmation.php` from session or DB rebuild |
| Invoice (auto) | `finalizePosReceiptInvoice()` at checkout | Proforma or final via `createAutoInvoiceForOrder()` |
| Invoice (manual) | `create-invoice-from-receipt` | Redirect to standard invoice create UI |
| Payments module | `views/payments/` | Additional receipts; may finalize invoice when fully paid |

